claim.claim-text:
9. An adjustable lid assembly for an oxygen mask dispensing container body, the lid assembly comprising:
a plate capable of being releasably attached to the container body;
a lid having at least one guide disposed thereon, the lid capable of moving relative to the plate along the guide;
a spring disposed between the lid and the plate; and,
a locking member operatively associated with the guide such that the position of the plate relative to the lid is manually adjustable against the force of the spring.
